  • Amazon Customer
    5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect seal with no bubbles and genuine protection
    Reviewed in the United Kingdom on 1 January 2025
    Size: iPhone 15 Pro 6.1-InchVerified Purchase
    Excellent protective case. I had previously had this protector and dropped a screw on my screen during DIY which chipped the protector. Initially thinking I had cracked my screen, the tempered glass had completely protected it and absorbed all the damage. I ordered another one to replace it, and peeling it off revealed the screen had suffered no damage whatsoever.

    Applying the new protector was very simple, it comes with detailed instructions and all the equipment you need to apply it easily and ensure no bubbles or dust getting underneath it (cloth, dust removal sticker, application frame). It also includes a squeegee item to push out any bubbles that do temporarily form which ensures a perfect fit.

    Additionally, it comes with two extra spare protectors, so if you make a mistake you can do it again or have spares for the future.
